@startuml
!define RECTANGLE class

package "Frontend (Browser)" {
  [HTMX (SPA)]
  [Bootstrap (CSS/JS)]
  [HTML Templates]
}

package "Backend (Django MTV)" {
  [urls.py] as router
  [views.py] as views
  [forms.py (ModelForm)] as forms
  [models.py] as models
}

database "SQLite3 / Database" {
  [Table: Usuarios]
  [Table: Auth_User]
}

[HTMX (SPA)] --> router : AJAX Requests (hx-boost)
router --> views : Routes to
views --> forms : Validates input (Regex)
views --> models : Query/Update
forms --> models : Binds to
models --> [Table: Usuarios] : ORM
models --> [Table: Auth_User] : ORM
views --> [HTML Templates] : Render (Context)
[HTML Templates] --> [Bootstrap (CSS/JS)] : Uses styles

note right of views
  **Design Patterns:**
  - **Decorators:** @login_required
  - **MVC / MTV:** Model-Template-View
end note

note right of forms
  **Design Patterns:**
  - **DRY:** ModelForm reuses model fields
end note
@enduml
